data.description: Welcome to this private quiet home that sits on 2.5 acres. Walk into the large entryway with large coat closet and access to the 3 car garage. The home features 2 bedrooms up both with walk-in closets, great kitchen dining and living room, and the large windows sharing the bright and wonderful wooded surroundings.  Downstairs family room has a glorious gas fireplace to warm everything inside. Large utility room along with another bedroom-and the 3 season porch to enjoy the privacy of the glorious trees and more.  Surround sound in the basement too.  This home could be yours!
